01:40:19,430 --> 01:40:21,524
Right! But don't you see?
对！还不明白吗？

1447
01:40:21,682 --> 01:40:24,982
She gonna go to her grave convincing folks this book ain't about Jackson.
她到死都不会让人知道这些事发生在Jackson

1448
01:40:25,144 --> 01:40:27,897
Now, that keeps us safe. Insured.
这样我们我就安全了，确保无疑

1449
01:40:29,232 --> 01:40:30,609
No.
不

1450
01:40:31,651 --> 01:40:32,994
No, that's too dangerous.
不，这样太危险了

1451
01:40:33,152 --> 01:40:35,496

1452
01:40:37,406 --> 01:40:40,785
Y'all two brought me into this, but I'm gonna finish it.
是你俩拉我进这淌浑水的，但我会了结此事的

1453
01:40:41,661 --> 01:40:45,006
Either put it in, or pull my parts out altogether. Y'all pick!
把那故事放进去，还是把我放进停尸房，你们选吧！

1454
01:40:47,375 --> 01:40:49,798

1455
01:40:56,425 --> 01:40:59,395
Thank you, Tommy. I should be out by 10:00. See you then.
谢谢，Tommy，我10点出来，到时见

1456
01:41:00,972 --> 01:41:02,940

1457
01:41:05,017 --> 01:41:08,692
This is Jolene French, reporting from the African Children's Benefit Ball,
我是Jolene French，在非洲儿童义卖舞会为您报道

1458
01:41:08,854 --> 01:41:12,199
and I'm here with League President, Miss Hilly Holbrook.
我身边的是社团主席，Hily小姐

1459
01:41:12,358 --> 01:41:16,864
Thanks, Jolene. And I'm just so excited for the auction tonight, aren't you?
谢谢，Jolene，我很兴奋拍卖马上就要开始了，你呢？

1460
01:41:17,029 --> 01:41:18,997
I'm absolutely thrilled.
我兴奋极了

1461
01:41:24,078 --> 01:41:25,079
Thank you.
谢谢

1462
01:41:34,880 --> 01:41:36,678
Hi!
嗨！

1463
01:41:36,841 --> 01:41:38,514

1464
01:41:38,676 --> 01:41:40,804

1465
01:41:43,681 --> 01:41:45,354
Did you see what Miss Celia got on?
你看到Celia小姐的那身衣服了吗？

1466
01:41:45,516 --> 01:41:48,690
Lord, have mercy. Women better hold onto their husbands tonight.
主，仁慈啊，女人今晚最好把老公都抓牢了

1467
01:41:48,853 --> 01:41:49,979

1468
01:41:50,146 --> 01:41:52,365
Miss Leefolt been working on that dress for four weeks
Leefolt小姐这四个礼拜都在弄她那件衣服

1469
01:41:52,523 --> 01:41:53,649
and that's what she came up with?
结果就弄成那样？

1470
01:41:53,816 --> 01:41:56,490
- Here.
给

1471
01:42:08,414 --> 01:42:09,586
Kiss me.
吻我

1472
01:42:43,574 --> 01:42:45,542
Everybody enjoying the evening?
大家今晚都尽兴吗？

1473
01:42:50,373 --> 01:42:53,377
Let's give a nice round of applause for the help.
先向帮佣们献上我们的掌声！

1474
01:42:57,129 --> 01:43:00,349
For all the men and women who have helped make tonight possible.
向帮助过今晚义卖的男男女女

1475
01:43:02,134 --> 01:43:04,978
A cause I'm sure is dear to their hearts as well.
她们无疑都有颗善良的心

1476
01:43:07,431 --> 01:43:09,559
- Your cocktail. - Thank you.
-你的鸡尾酒 -谢谢

1477
01:43:11,185 --> 01:43:15,361
Honey, don't you think you've had enough to drink?
亲爱的，你不觉得今晚你喝得有点太多了吗？

1478
01:43:15,523 --> 01:43:17,241
I wish you'd try and eat something.
你最好吃点东西

1479
01:43:17,400 --> 01:43:19,619
I'm not having my stomach poke out.
我是不会让自己吐的

1480
01:43:23,531 --> 01:43:27,411
OK, OK, everybody, quiet down. I got the list of the winners!
好，大家，请安静，我要公布今晚的赢家了

1481
01:43:29,537 --> 01:43:30,789
OK.
好

1482
01:43:30,955 --> 01:43:35,711
The winner of the beautiful mink car coat is...
最美貂皮大衣的得主是...

1483
01:43:36,377 --> 01:43:37,594
...Charlotte Phelan!

1484
01:43:39,463 --> 01:43:41,215
- Congrats, Miss Phelan.
- 恭喜，Phelan小姐

1485
01:43:41,382 --> 01:43:43,555
Ladies, I hope your husbands take note of that.
小姐们，希望你们的老公都记下

1486
01:43:45,094 --> 01:43:48,519
Now it's time for the baked goods.
现在，该烘烤食物出场了

1487
01:43:49,724 --> 01:43:51,647
Ooh, yummy, yummy!
哦，好吃，好吃！

1488
01:43:51,809 --> 01:43:55,029
The highest bid in baked goods goes to
烘烤食物类最高拍价得主是

1489
01:43:55,187 --> 01:43:58,031
Minny Jackson's chocolate pie.
Minny Jackson的巧克力派

1490
01:43:59,817 --> 01:44:01,319
Congratulations...
恭喜...

1491
01:44:01,986 --> 01:44:03,704
...Hilly Holbrook!
...买主是Hilly Holbrook！

1492
01:44:04,071 --> 01:44:08,247
- Oh! Hilly. - That's funny.
-哦！Hilly -真有趣

1493
01:44:08,409 --> 01:44:10,082
I didn't bid on anything.
我什么都没拍

1494
01:44:10,244 --> 01:44:13,794
All right. And now it's time for Danica's strawberry jam.
好，接下来是Danica的草莓果酱

1495
01:44:13,956 --> 01:44:15,208
Shh!
嘘！

1496
01:44:17,918 --> 01:44:19,795
Congratulations, Hilly!
恭喜，Hily！

1497
01:44:19,962 --> 01:44:23,091
I didn't know you were a fan of Minny's pies.
我不知道你这么喜欢Minny的派

1498
01:44:24,675 --> 01:44:27,144
I've been wanting to talk to you all night.
今晚我一直想和你谈谈

1499
01:44:27,303 --> 01:44:29,271
Minny said why you won't be my friend.
Minny告诉我 你为什么不愿做我朋友了

1500
01:44:29,430 --> 01:44:31,683
It's 'cause you think me and Johnny went behind your back.
因为你认为当初我和Johnny背着你偷情

1501
01:44:33,350 --> 01:44:35,273
- Wait. I want to talk...
-等等，我想说...

1502
01:44:35,436 --> 01:44:36,813
Oh, no.
哦，不

1503
01:44:36,979 --> 01:44:38,652
I'm so sorry.
对不起

1504
01:44:41,859 --> 01:44:43,611
Come here, sweetheart.
过来，甜心

1505
01:44:43,778 --> 01:44:45,530
Let me bring you back to your table.
我带你回你的桌子去

1506
01:44:47,990 --> 01:44:50,459
- I'm really sorry. - it's all right. Don't worry about it.
-真是抱歉 -没关系，别放在心上

1507
01:44:51,744 --> 01:44:55,339
What are you trying to do to me? What are you and that nigra up to?
你想对我干什么？你和那黑鬼在捣什么鬼？

1508
01:44:55,498 --> 01:44:57,171
I don't know what you're talking about.
我不明白你的意思

1509
01:44:57,333 --> 01:44:58,880
You liar! Who did you tell?
你撒谎！你都告诉谁了？

1510
01:44:59,043 --> 01:45:01,341
Hilly, I got pregnant after you and Johnny broke up!
Hily，在你和Johnny分手后我才怀孕的！

1511
01:45:01,504 --> 01:45:04,178
- Oh, shit! - Shut up, Mother!
-哦，我去！ -闭嘴，妈妈！

1512
01:45:04,340 --> 01:45:07,765
Johnny never cheated on you.
Johnny从没背着你搞外遇

1513
01:45:08,677 --> 01:45:10,179
At least not with me.
至少不是和我

1514
01:45:10,346 --> 01:45:13,725
Oh, Johnny would never cheat on me.
哦，Johnny绝不会背着我搞外遇的

1515
01:45:13,891 --> 01:45:17,270
I'm so sorry! I thought you'd be tickled you won that pie!
抱歉！我以为赢下那个派你会很高兴，！

1516
01:45:18,145 --> 01:45:22,525
You tell that nigra, if she tells anybody, I will make her suffer!
你告诉那黑奴，她要敢告诉其他人，我就让她生不如死

1517
01:45:22,691 --> 01:45:24,989
Hey, that is enough.
嘿，够了

1518
01:45:25,569 --> 01:45:26,570
Celia.

1519
01:45:26,737 --> 01:45:28,239
Hey, baby, what's the matter?
嗨，宝贝，怎么了？

1520
01:45:32,034 --> 01:45:33,035
Oh!
哦！

1521
01:45:34,662 --> 01:45:37,962
Oh, shit. What a mess. Napkins.
哦，我去，一团糟，拿餐巾纸来

1522
01:45:39,458 --> 01:45:42,132
Why don't we get back to the auction?
为什么我们不回到拍卖上来？

1523
01:45:42,294 --> 01:45:45,218
- Next up, Debby's peppermint bark. - Celia!
-下一个是Debby的薄荷脆皮

1524
01:45:45,798 --> 01:45:47,846
It goes great with hot cocoa.
和热可可是绝配

1525
01:45:53,722 --> 01:45:55,941
Oh, just come on home with us tonight, Mother.
哦，今晚和我们一起回家吧，妈妈

1526
01:45:56,100 --> 01:45:59,354
No, thanks. I've got a pie to eat.
不用，谢谢，我还要吃派呢

1527
01:45:59,520 --> 01:46:01,943
You throw that pie away right now.
你马上把那派给扔了

1528
01:46:02,106 --> 01:46:04,234
I spent good money on this pie.
这派我可花了大价才买下的

1529
01:46:05,150 --> 01:46:06,948
I won it just for you.
特意为你买的

1530
01:46:07,111 --> 01:46:09,239
You signed me up?
你冒名替我？

1531
01:46:09,405 --> 01:46:13,455
I may have trouble remembering my own name, or what country I live in,
我也许会记不清自己的名字，生活在哪个国家

1532
01:46:13,617 --> 01:46:16,040
but there are two things I can't seem to forget:
但有两件事我记得很清楚

1533
01:46:16,203 --> 01:46:19,753
that my own daughter threw me into a nursing home,
就是我的亲生女儿送我进养老院

1534
01:46:19,915 --> 01:46:21,917
and that she ate Minny's shit.
还有她吃了Minny的便便

1535
01:46:23,002 --> 01:46:24,174
Good night.
晚安

1536
01:46:28,382 --> 01:46:31,852
- Hey, how about a nightcap? - Let's go.
-嗨，睡前再来一杯？ -走吧

1537
01:46:38,976 --> 01:46:42,150
I'm not right for this kind of life, Minny
我不适合这样的生活，Minny

1538
01:46:44,023 --> 01:46:47,197
I don't need a dining room table for 12 people.
我不需要一张能坐下12人的餐桌

1539
01:46:48,027 --> 01:46:51,406
I couldn't get two people over here if I begged.
即便我乞讨也拉不来两个人

1540
01:46:55,701 --> 01:46:58,045
I can't do this to Johnny anymore.
我再也不能这样对Johnny了

1541
01:47:00,456 --> 01:47:02,754
That's why I've gotta go back to Sugar Ditch.
所以我打算搬回Sugar Ditch

1542
01:47:04,460 --> 01:47:06,679
You can't move back to Sugar Ditch.
你不能搬回Sugar Ditch

1543
01:47:08,923 --> 01:47:10,971
Lord.
主啊

1544
01:47:11,634 --> 01:47:13,932
I reckon it's time you knew.
是时候让你知道了

1545
01:47:14,094 --> 01:47:15,266
Sit down.
坐下

1546
01:47:25,981 --> 01:47:29,030
So Miss Hilly thought you knew about the terrible awful.
所以Hily小姐以为你知道这件可怕的事

1547
01:47:30,319 --> 01:47:32,321
That you was making fun of her.
以为你在取乐她

1548
01:47:35,324 --> 01:47:37,873
It's my fault she pounced on you.
她这样对你是我的错

1549
01:47:40,371 --> 01:47:42,373
If you leave Mr. Johnny...
如果你离开Johnny先生

1550
01:47:44,708 --> 01:47:47,803
...then Miss Hilly done won the whole ball game.
...那么这次舞会Hily就真赢了

1551
01:47:49,964 --> 01:47:51,807
Then she done beaten me...
然后她也赢了我...

1552
01:47:53,217 --> 01:47:55,311
...and she done beat you.
...她赢了你

1553
01:48:02,351 --> 01:48:04,900
Thank you for telling me that.
谢谢你告诉我这些

1554
01:48:12,403 --> 01:48:16,033
Lord, look at all these pages. 266.
天，看这书厚的，266页

1555
01:48:16,490 --> 01:48:18,367
Mm-mm!
嗯！

1556
01:48:19,618 --> 01:48:22,497
So we just send it off? Just wait and see?
接下来我们把它寄出去？就等着瞧了？

1557
01:48:22,663 --> 01:48:24,381
Hope Miss Stein gonna publish it?
等Stein小姐出版它？

1558
01:48:24,540 --> 01:48:28,670
Well, I have one more story to type before I put it in the mail,
在放进信箱前我还有一个故事要写

1559
01:48:28,836 --> 01:48:30,338
but other than that, we're done.
除此之外，我们都完事了

1560
01:48:30,504 --> 01:48:32,097
Which one you got left?
还有哪个故事要写？

1561
01:48:34,591 --> 01:48:35,763
Uh, mine.
我的

1562
01:48:46,395 --> 01:48:48,864
I need to talk to you about Constantine.
我要和你谈谈Constantine

1563
01:48:49,356 --> 01:48:53,361
Oh, Eugenia, that was so long ago.
哦，Eugenia，那是多久之前的事了

1564
01:48:53,902 --> 01:48:55,074
What happened?
发生了什么？

1565
01:48:55,237 --> 01:48:57,615
Oh. 
哦

1566
01:48:58,407 --> 01:49:00,250
What happened?
发生了什么？

1567
01:49:04,997 --> 01:49:07,125
She didn't give me a choice.
她让我别无选择

1568
01:49:12,254 --> 01:49:17,181
The Daughters of America had just appointed me state regent.
Daughters of America刚任命我为state regent

1569
01:49:19,970 --> 01:49:23,315
Grace Higginbotham, our esteemed president, came all the way down
备受尊敬的主席Grace Higginbotham为了颁奖典礼

1570
01:49:23,474 --> 01:49:27,445
from Washington, D.C., to our house for the ceremony.
一路从华盛顿赶来

1571
01:49:29,063 --> 01:49:33,068
- That's just beautiful. Look at that.
真是漂亮，快瞧瞧

1572
01:49:36,570 --> 01:49:40,291
She'd gotten so old and slow, Skeeter.
她又老又笨拙，Skeeter

1573
01:49:43,994 --> 01:49:45,211
Yes, ma'am.
是的，女人

1574
01:49:47,873 --> 01:49:51,298
It's such an honor that you came all this way.
真是荣幸，您大老远跑来

1575
01:50:00,010 --> 01:50:01,057
That's all right.
好了

1576
01:50:05,891 --> 01:50:08,565
- Hello, Miss Charlotte.
你好，Charlotte小姐

1577
01:50:10,604 --> 01:50:12,732
We were expecting you next week.
还以为你下礼拜才到

1578
01:50:12,898 --> 01:50:14,696
I decided to come early and surprise Mama.
我决定早点过来给妈妈个惊喜

1579
01:50:14,858 --> 01:50:16,781
- Oh.
哦

1580
01:50:17,820 --> 01:50:19,197
I'm entertaining.
我在宴请呢

1581
01:50:19,363 --> 01:50:21,741
Why don't you go around back. Wait in the kitchen.
你先绕路到后面厨房等着

1582
01:50:27,412 --> 01:50:28,709
Go on now.
快走

1583
01:50:31,875 --> 01:50:33,377
I am sorry.
抱歉

1584
01:50:36,338 --> 01:50:38,966
- Rachel, what are you doing?
-Rachel，你这是干什么？

1585
01:50:39,133 --> 01:50:42,387
I'm just doing as I was told, Miss Charlotte.
我不是在照你的吩咐做吗，Charlotte小姐

1586
01:50:42,553 --> 01:50:44,055
Going to the kitchen.
去厨房

1587
01:50:44,221 --> 01:50:46,315
But I'm going to see my mama first.
但我要先见妈妈

1588
01:50:47,766 --> 01:50:50,519
- Hello, Mama.
-你好，妈妈

1589
01:50:50,686 --> 01:50:53,405
Go on to the kitchen, baby. I'll be there directly.
去厨房，宝贝，我马上就来

1590
01:50:53,564 --> 01:50:57,740
You may put up with this kind of nonsense, but I do not.
这荒唐事是可忍，孰不可忍也

1591
01:51:04,449 --> 01:51:05,996
Get out of this house, Rachel.
滚出这房子，Rachel

1592
01:51:10,122 --> 01:51:12,500
You heard her. Go on, girl.
你听到她说的了，快走吧，女孩

1593
01:51:12,666 --> 01:51:16,796
Miss Charlotte, let me take her to the kitchen. Come on, baby. Let's go.
Charlotte小姐，让我带她到厨房，来，宝贝，我们走

1594
01:51:18,672 --> 01:51:20,094
Charlotte.

1595
01:51:24,511 --> 01:51:26,434
Both of you.
你们俩

1596
01:51:26,597 --> 01:51:29,225
Leave. Now.
都走，现在

1597
01:51:33,395 --> 01:51:34,738
Come on, Mama.
走，妈妈

1598
01:52:07,262 --> 01:52:08,809
Come on now.
走吧

1599
01:52:22,444 --> 01:52:24,947
Constantine didn't do anything wrong.
Constantine并没做错

1600
01:52:26,657 --> 01:52:28,580
And you love Rachel. I know you do.
而你爱Rachel，我知道的

1601
01:52:28,742 --> 01:52:31,916
She was our president. What was I supposed to do?
她可是我们主席，我能怎么办？

1602
01:52:32,913 --> 01:52:37,259
She did you the biggest favor of your life. She taught me everything.
她帮了你人生一个大忙，她教我长大成人

1603
01:52:37,417 --> 01:52:40,591
Well, you idolized her too much. You always have.
你太崇拜她了，你总是这样

1604
01:52:40,754 --> 01:52:42,882
I needed someone to look up to.
我总要崇拜某人的

1605
01:52:46,301 --> 01:52:47,678
Well, I...
这个，我...

1606
01:52:48,512 --> 01:52:52,187
I went to her house the next day, but she had already gone.
第二天我就上她家，但她已经走了

1607
01:53:22,921 --> 01:53:24,468
How could you not tell me all this?
你怎能瞒着我这事？

1608
01:53:24,631 --> 01:53:28,135
Because I didn't want to upset you during your final exams.
那时你就要期末考了 我不想打扰你

1609
01:53:28,302 --> 01:53:31,021
I knew you'd blame me, and it wasn't my fault!
我知道你会怪我，但不是我的错！

1610
01:53:31,179 --> 01:53:32,772
I have to go find her. She needs me.
我要去找她，她需要我

1611
01:53:32,931 --> 01:53:34,228
- Eugenia. - What?
-Eugenia -什么？

1612
01:53:36,143 --> 01:53:39,613
We sent your brother up to Chicago to bring Constantine home.
我们让你哥哥去芝加哥接Constantine回家

1613
01:53:48,530 --> 01:53:49,952
When he got there...
当他到达时...

1614
01:53:54,036 --> 01:53:55,583
...she had died.
...她已经去世了

1615
01:54:11,720 --> 01:54:13,814
You broke her heart.
你伤透了她的心

1616
01:54:19,394 --> 01:54:24,321
I'm...I'm sorry. I'm so sorry!
对不起，对不起

1617
01:54:27,402 --> 01:54:29,029
I'm sorry.
对不起

1618
01:55:24,835 --> 01:55:26,803
They printed a few thousand copies
他们印制了几千本

1619
01:55:26,962 --> 01:55:30,307
with the worst advance Miss Stein had ever seen.
Stein小姐没见过比这更糟的发行预售

1620
01:55:30,465 --> 01:55:33,093
Baby, what you doing with Alicia book? You can't read.
